title: Goodbye Charlie 1964 Movie
description:
Goodbye Charlie (1964)

Shot by a jealous husband, Charley falls out a porthole and is lost at sea only to find himself returned as an attractive blond woman. His best friend is staying at his house as he puts Charlie&#039;s affairs in order and after being convinced, finds himself an unwilling helper in Charlie&#039;s new plan to marry into money.
